    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family of mammals containing only two living members, the giraffe and the okapi, with many diverse extinct species formerly spread throughout Eurasia and Africa.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
